{"tid":2156101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"狀元：港曙光正消逝  憧憬中大修讀理學 籲勇於明志","createTime":"2020-08-14T08:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T09:15:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd3a0a47d88229481578872c5561715c21cee74","tid":2156101,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:35:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/CZPFZ3VUFVDSZAHYF6LZCHQOWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FCZPFZ3VUFVDSZAHYF6LZCHQOWU%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=75c5e0cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FCZPFZ3VUFVDSZAHYF6LZCHQOWU%2F&h=8fb3267b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/CZPFZ3VUFVDSZAHYF6LZCHQOWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n狀元：港曙光正消逝 <br />\n憧憬中大修讀理學 籲勇於明志<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fy_aBKfUnvl5ui7q49sT2VVmXW0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TUTNS3UFTBDSXBBQD3QSHJ72BA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffy_aBKfUnvl5ui7q49sT2VVmXW0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTUTNS3UFTBDSXBBQD3QSHJ72BA.jpg&h=5386afda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃摯毅<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早前以「竊鉤者誅、竊國者侯」形容香港現況的聖保羅男女中學狀元黃摯毅，昨如願獲中大理學（細胞及分子生物學）取錄。。。。。。。。。。勉勵港人應保存個人意志，力求和而不同。他關注近日《蘋果》被搜事件，希望港人珍視言論自由，勇於表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港大設200萬新生獎學金<br />\n<br />\n黃摯毅昨接受本。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n近日社會環境令他感到香港的曙光正在消逝。港版國安法實施後，他更感到學者以至市民批評政府的空間收窄，擔心會影響學術自由，「例如做研究會講求攞資金，會唔會資金同政治立場掛鈎呢？」又指沈祖堯等知名本地學者近日離港發展，或可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n冀社會尊重不同立場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i3HdgJYmgyYliw3Vq_S1KX9dYv4=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7PFJGESZWZDORNPK5RI2TPQJWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi3HdgJYmgyYliw3Vq_S1KX9dYv4%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7PFJGESZWZDORNPK5RI2TPQJWM.jpg&h=e922b8e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聖保羅男女中學狀元黃摯毅如願獲中大理學（細胞及分子生物學）取錄。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n黃期望政府或大學應消除學者對香港學術自由感擔憂的因素，包括社會氛圍，「知識分子要留低，你個社會氛圍一定要有利自由、有利民主，唔同嘅普世價值。」<br />\n<br />\n他認為港人更應珍視言論自由，勇於表達個人想法，「一個社會最可貴嘅就係多元化，即使你係小粉紅、你係黃絲、你係藍絲，甚至你係綠絲都好，一個社會可以尊重每個人立場，畀唔同立場嘅人都存在，呢個先係最好嘅社會，如果社會係一體化，淨係得某個立場，都唔會係一個好嘅社會。」他最近亦關注蘋果大樓被搜查，認為《蘋果》是一間敢言媒體。<br />\n<br />\n至於未來完成學業後，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他又引用北宋名臣韓愈《爭臣論》中的「君子居其位，則思死其官。未得位，則思修其辭以明其道。我將以明道也，非以為直而加人也。」贈予港人，意思是作為君子身於官位，就應有以身殉職的思想準備；未在官位者，則應考慮修飾文辭來闡明其掌握的道理。而所謂闡明道理，並非自以為正直而強迫人家接受自己的一套。<br />\n<br />\n他望港人恪守信念，當遇到不公勇於發聲，「人遇到不平嘅事就要講出你嘅看法，哪怕你講嘅是對是錯，係比人低或比人高尚，因為呢個係人喺社會上應做嘅角色。」"},{"pid":"db4b5f111f1b4e4c18224fe113432946d84a20cb","tid":2156101,"uid":189109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"黃生好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d310366e1158fadefde322ed1b089fcff04fd051","tid":2156101,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"手足小心"},{"pid":"14c1159bbb4bc1b01b4cf1523bbd22e98610c961","tid":2156101,"uid":50180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真狀元 有文人風骨<br />\n可惜唔知呢個社會容唔容得下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6d41546fe3e0d4c9b5801a427e8267693ad448","tid":2156101,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class